text: Liana Dance (born 18 April 1998) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. and 2016 FINA World Women's Youth Water Polo Championships. == References == ==Other websites== * lianadance nzwomenswaterpolo Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
